  "text": "The few conclusive results and non-controversial data have not overcome the difficulties that have prevented previous attempts to establish a policy or guide for RBCT. Despite these limitations and the lack of definitive answers, doctors often have no other choice but the consensus guidelines [CITATION_1] .",
